1) Create a function to calculate a*b+log(a); use it to get calc(3,4) and calc(5,6)
calcLog <-function(a, b){
  return (a*b+log(a))
}
2) Create a function to check if the number is divisible by three or not
divBy3 <- function(val){
  result <- FALSE
  if(val %% 3 == 0){
    result == 3
  }
  return (result)
}
